name: Radiant Light
description:
Radiant Light

This is my mix of models for creating wonderful illustrations in the anime style. The mix is perfect for illustrations.

Be sure to use Negative Embedding (for example: AuroraNegative, KHFB, EasyNegative 2, ng_deepnegative, verybadimagenegative, badhandv4, and etc)

According to my observations, the second version more accurately conveys the BUNBUN/abec style, but the first version has more colorful special effects of light and shadow.

Updates

  • 02.07.2023 - Radiant Light V2 released.

  • 02.07.2023 - Added safetensor format Radiant Light V1

  • 11.06.2023 - Radiant Light V1 released.

This is mix based on models:

V1:

  • Counterfeit-V3.0 - v3.0 | Stable Diffusion Checkpoint | Civitai

  • Pika's New Generation - v2.0 | Stable Diffusion Checkpoint | Civitai

  • 【Style】 Illustrator Style BUNBUN | abec | LoRA - BUNBUN_style | Stable Diffusion LoRA | Civitai

V2:

  • HoloKuki

  • 【Checkpoint】YesMix

  • Mymix

  • Pika's New Generation - v2.0 | Stable Diffusion Checkpoint | Civitai

  • 【Style】 Illustrator Style BUNBUN | abec | LoRA - BUNBUN_style | Stable Diffusion LoRA | Civitai

  • BUNBUN/abec Style LoRA

Recommended parameters:

  • Resolution: 512x768 / 768x512

  • Sampling method: DDIM / Euler a / DPM++ SDE, 2M, 2M SDE

  • Sampling steps: >20

  • CFG Scale: 7

  • Clip Skip: 2

  • HiresFix: ON

  • Denoising strength: 0.3-0.6

  • Upscaler: SwinIR / Valar / Remacri / AnimeSharp / any

  • VAE: pastel-waifu-diffusion.vae / kl-f8-anime2 VAE / Any Anime

Thank you very much:

  • Aotsuyu for HoloKuki

  • zakp for YesMix

  • lama_guanicoe for Mymix

  • PikaDesigner for Pika's New Generation

  • Lykon for BUNBUN/abec Style LoRA

  • BUNBUN/abec for GREAT illustrations

Looking forward to your feedback.
